author: Jo Khan
title: There's a lot of coronavirus research, here are some studies worth reading
description: While much of the world slows down, or shuts down, in response to the COVID-19 pandemic, many scientists are busy crunching what data they have on the virus to try to understand it better. Here's a summary of the latest research.
